import React from "react";
import {Box, Button, Select, MenuItem} from '@material-ui/core'

export default (props) =>{
    return (
        <Box>
            <Select disableUnderline variant="filled" defaultValue="Online">
                <MenuItem value="Online">Online</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="Offline">Offline</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="Hybrid">Hybrid</MenuItem>
            </Select>
            <Select disableUnderline variant="filled" defaultValue="Remote">
                <MenuItem value="Remote">Online</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="Office">Offline</MenuItem>
            </Select>
            <Button  variant="contained" color="primary" disableElevation>
            Search
          </Button>
        </Box>
    )
}
